title: Flight Simulator 2020 - POI's - Dune Ornithopter  free fall above Washington DC
description:
In this short we are flying over using the Dune Ornithopter and perform a free fall above Washington DC. During the fall we can see the Pentagon and when almost hitting the ground we do a low altitude flight over the Jefferson Memorial.
